{
  "text": "While the causes of adolescent alcohol and substance use are related to various factors, media plays a key role. Advertising for smoking or alcohol brands especially as sponsorship of popular and sports events, distribution of free sam- [CITATION_1] , promoting an attractive image of smokers with high influence over our youth. Almost 25% of male students in all schools reported using ecstasy products, to a larger extent in HPS which was very alarming. Not only the practice is hazardous to health, cessation is very difficult when this becomes addictive and its consequences on the life of the adolescent and his family are detrimental.",
